Drop‑in security module

• security/piratebay-block/denylist.txt• Label: Domains and wildcard patterns
thepiratebay.*
piratebay.*
proxybay.*
piratebayproxy.*
tpbproxy.*
thepiratebayproxy.*
pirateproxy.*
torrentbay.*
torrent‑mirror.*

• security/piratebay-block/hosts.example• Label: 0.0.0.0 mappings for local devices
0.0.0.0 thepiratebay.org
0.0.0.0 piratebay.org
0.0.0.0 proxybay.*

• security/piratebay-block/uBlock-origin.txt• Label: Browser filter rules
||thepiratebay.^
||piratebay.^
||proxybay.^
||pirateproxy.^

• security/piratebay-block/nextdns.yaml• Label: Category blocks + custom deny
categories: [piracy, p2p, adult, suspicious]
denylist:• thepiratebay.*
• piratebay.*
• proxybay.*
• pirateproxy.*




