Infinity Sponge loop wiring

• framework/infinity_sponge/loop.py• Label: Backwards pass, sponge absorb, finalize/quarantine

• framework/infinity_sponge/examples/run.py• Label: Minimal runnable demo over sample logs

• ops/run_sponge.py• Label: Ingests denylist updates, runs loop, writes digest
• Emits report: ops/reports/sponge_report.json

• ops/reports/.keep to keep the folder in Git


---

CI and scheduled containment

• .github/workflows/containment.yml• Label: Nightly job to refresh mirrors, run sponge, commit digest



name: containment
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: "0 3 * * *"   # nightly UTC
  workflow_dispatch:
jobs:
  refresh-and-scan:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout
        uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Setup Python
        uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with:
          python-version: "3.11"
      - name: Install deps
        run: pip install -r requirements.txt || true
      - name: Run sponge loop
        run: python ops/run_sponge.py
      - name: Commit report
        run: |
          git config user.name "Containment Bot"
          git config user.email "bot@spaceleaf.example"
          git add ops/reports/sponge_report.json
          git commit -m "Nightly containment digest"
          git push


• ops/requirements.txt• Label: Keep it lean (json, hashlib are stdlib; no heavy deps)



